lead_paragraph: Former Wallaby Glen Ella has fired a warning to his compatriots ahead of the end-of-season showdown with England at Twickenham on Saturday - Eddie Jones's team are better than they were in June.

headline.print_headline: England Are Better Than Team That Swept Wallabies in June-Ella
